sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% ================================
    %% Definisi Aktor & Partisipan (MVC)
    %% ================================
    actor User as Pelapor (User)
    participant View as View (Blade Form)
    participant Controller as ComplaintController
    participant Model as Model: Complaint
    participant PhotoModel as Model: ComplaintPhoto

    %% ================================
    %% Alur Pengiriman Form Pengaduan
    %% ================================
    User->>View: Mengisi form (Judul, Lokasi, dll) & klik "Kirim"
    View->>Controller: POST /complaints (data form & file foto)
    activate Controller

    Note right of Controller: Validasi input (Request->validate)

    alt Validasi Gagal
        Controller-->>View: redirect()->back() dengan session errors
        View-->>User: Tampilkan pesan error (merah) pada form
    else Validasi Berhasil
        Controller->>Model: Complaint::create([data])
        activate Model
        Model-->>Controller: Return objek $complaint (dengan ID baru)
        deactivate Model

        opt Lampiran Foto Tersedia
            Note right of Controller: Simpan file ke Storage (folder public)
            Controller->>PhotoModel: ComplaintPhoto::create([complaint_id, path])
            activate PhotoModel
            PhotoModel-->>Controller: Return success
            deactivate PhotoModel
        end

        Controller-->>View: redirect() ke Daftar Pengaduan + flash message success
        View-->>User: Tampilkan notifikasi "Berhasil Disimpan"
    end

    deactivate Controller